hotel_data.hotel_description: Less than 500 metres from the famous shops of Ginza, Mercure Hotel features concierge services and comfortable rooms with free Wi-Fi. Aromatherapy treatments are available at a charge.
hotel_data.hotel_important_information: Guests are required to show a photo identification and credit card upon check-in. Please note that all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply. An accommodation tax per person per night is not included in the price and needs to be paid at the property.
hotel_data.name: Mercure Hotel Ginza Tokyo

hotel_data.hotelier_welcome_message:
Strategically located in the heart of Tokyo, close to places of tourist interest and Central Business District. Easy access to Tokyo Metro Station and Airport Limousine Bus.

Our Club InterContinental Lounge is unique to the city, offering unparalleled levels of service and sweeping views of Tokyo and Mt. Fuji, whilst located away from the bustling metropolis below on level 35 of the hotel. The Club Lounge is a perfect retreat whether it be for business or leisure and offers the following exclusive benefits:

Personalised welcome and departure service in the Lounge
Gourmet continental breakfast daily
Afternoon refreshments
Evening cocktails with hot and cold snacks and canapes
Use of our private meeting room for up to two hours (subject to availability) with custom built video-conferencing system
All day refreshments
Personalized Club InterContinental concierge and business services
Shower facilities
hotel_data.hotel_description: ANA InterContinental Tokyo is located in Tokyos Ark Hills, a minutes walk from Tameike-sanno and Roppongi-itchome Subway Stations. The hotel houses 844 guest rooms, 12 dining options and 22 event halls.
hotel_data.name: ANA InterContinental Tokyo
hotel_data.hotel_important_information: An accommodation tax per person per night is not included in the price and needs to be paid at the property. Swimming pool is closed from Mon 09 Sept 2019 until Sun 31 May 2020 The Airport Limousine Bus is available to/from Haneda and Narita International Airport to the hotel. Please contact the property in advance if you are traveling with multiple children. Rooms have a maximum capacity of 3 persons (including children) per room. For more information, please contact the property directly. Please note that the hotel will undergo a scheduled power outage due to facility inspections and electric facilities including WiFi, air conditioning, lifts and hot water supply will be out of service on the following dates/times: 06 January 2020, 00:30-04:30 in the morning.

hotel_data.hotel_description: Located near the central Shibuya area, the b tokyo sangenjaya is a 2-minute walk from Sangenjaya Station, just 2 stops from Shibuya Station on the Tokyu Den-en-Toshi Line.
hotel_data.name: the b tokyo sangenjaya
hotel_data.hotel_important_information: An accommodation tax per person per night is not included in the price and needs to be paid at the property. Please note that the guest name on the reservation must be the same as the name on the card used to make the booking. The credit card used to make the booking must be presented at the time of check in. <Regarding Item Postage and Delivery> - The hotel cannot accept nor store any commercial goods, including goods purchased online (packages, boxes, bags, cartons, gifts or similar items) unless the recipient is registered and is staying at the hotel. - Any delivery purchased online and arriving at the hotel during the guests' stay must be accepted and signed by the guest in person. The hotel cannot take any liability for payment, damage or loss of the delivery item on behalf of the guest. - The hotel does not feature any storage space. Please notify the hotel in advance of the quantity of items expected and of any large-size items. - For disposal of bulk items or large quantities of packaging / wrapping material the hotel reserves the right to charge additional fees.

hotel_data.hotel_description: An official hotel of Tokyo Disney Resort, Sheraton Tokyo Bay offers indoor and outdoor pools, specialty Disney shops, a kids play area and 4 dining options.
hotel_data.name: Sheraton Grande Tokyo Bay Hotel
hotel_data.hotel_important_information: Guests are required to show a photo identification and credit card upon check-in. Please note that all Special Requests are subject to availability and additional charges may apply. Guests with tattoos may not be permitted to use the propertys public bathing areas or other facilities where the tattoos might be visible to other guests. There is a luggage drop-off service at the hotel's service counter at JR Maihama Station. Guests can drop off their luggage anytime between 08:00-15:00 at the service counter at the station and it will be delivered to the hotel. Children - Please note that children 6 years and younger can use an existing bed free of charge when staying with an adult. Please note, only 1 child is accepted per bed, per adult. - Please note, breakfast for children 4 years and older is not included in the rates. Additional charges will apply. Facilities - Tickets to Tokyo Disney Resort can be purchased at the hotel's ticket counter, open 06:00-20:00. - Please note, the property's seasonal outdoor swimming pool, public bath and sauna facility are available at an additional charge. The property's indoor swimming pool and fitness room can be used free of charge. - On-site parking is available on a first-come, first-serve basis and is subject to availability. - Family Rooms are non-smoking only.

hotel_data.hotel_description: Located in the heart of Tokyo, just a few steps away from Ginza, the world-famous shopping and entertainment district. Conrad Tokyo boasts rooms furnished with modern decor, award winning restaurants and a 29th-floor spa with beautiful city views.
hotel_data.name: Conrad Tokyo
hotel_data.hotel_important_information: Fitness centre is closed from Mon 06 Jan 2020 until Fri 10 Jan 2020 Spa/wellness centre is closed from Mon 06 Jan 2020 until Fri 10 Jan 2020 Due to limited availability, guests planning to use an extra bed are requested to contact the hotel in advance. The pool is open from 06:00 until 22:00, with last admission at 21:30. Children (aged 4 to 15) may use the pool from 09:00 until 19:00. Please note the pool and fitness centre will be temporarily closed due to facility inspections on the following dates/times: - Pool: 06 January 2020 until 10 January 2020. - Fitness centre: 06 January 2020 until 07 January 2020, 09:00-15:00.
